    {
      "scene_index": 5,
      "label": "第五场",
      "characters_present": [
        "四老军",
        "探子",
        "杨继业"
      ],
      "lines": [
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（四老军扛刀、抬弓引杨继业同上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨继业",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "叹杨家秉忠心大宋扶保，"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨继业",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "到如今只落得兵败荒郊。"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨继业",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "擅敢夺我主爷锦绣龙朝。"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨继业",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我父子倒做了马前英豪。"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨继业",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "只杀得血成河鬼哭神嚎。"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨继业",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "二郎儿短剑下命赴阴曹；"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨继业",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "四、八郎失番邦无有下梢；"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨继业",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "七郎儿被潘洪射死芭蕉。"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨继业",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "可叹他尽得忠又尽孝、身披铠甲、南征北剿、昼夜杀砍、马不停蹄、为国勤劳。"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨继业",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我的儿呀！"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨继业",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "一家人只落得无有下梢。"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨继业",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "请我主到五台快乐逍遥。"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨继业",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "四下里众番奴有如海潮。"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨继业",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "一杆枪保圣驾闯出笼牢。"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨继业",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "那时我东杀西砍、左冲右撞、虎撞羊群、被困在两狼山，内无有粮、外无有草、"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨继业",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "盼兵不到、盼子不归、眼见得我这老残生就难以还朝。"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨继业",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我的儿呀！"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨继业",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "恨北国萧银宗打来战表"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨继业",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "贼潘洪在金殿帅印挂了"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨继业",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "金沙滩双龙会一阵败了"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨继业",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "大郎儿替宋主把忠尽了"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨继业",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "杨三郎被马踏尸骨难找"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨继业",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "杨五郎在五台削发修道"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨继业",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "只剩下六郎儿随营征讨"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨继业",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "可叹我八个子四子丧了，把四子丧了"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨继业",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "方良臣与潘洪又生计巧"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨继业",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "又谁知中了那奸贼圈套"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨继业",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "多亏了杨延昭一马来到"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨继业",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "有老夫领人马夜来战道"
        },
        {
          "character": "四老军",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "饿呀！"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨继业",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "饥饿了就该把战马砍倒！"
        },
        {
          "character": "四老军",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "冷啊！"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨继业",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "身寒冷就该把帐棚焚烧。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（空中雁鸣。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "四老军",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "雁来了！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（杨继业打雁，弓折弦断。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨继业",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "宝雕弓打不着空中飞鸟，"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨继业",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "弓又折弦又断为的哪条？"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（探子上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "探子",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "报！战马被石虎咬倒。"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨继业",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "不好了！"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨继业",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "恨石虎把我的战马咬倒，"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨继业",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "为大将无良骑怎把兵交？"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨继业",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "找一个避风所再作计较。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（杨继业、四老军同下。）"
        }
      ],
      "interactions": [
