    {
      "scene_index": 6,
      "label": "第六场",
      "characters_present": [
        "杨继业",
        "老丈",
        "苏武",
        "韩延寿"
      ],
      "lines": [
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（苏武上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "苏武",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "吾乃汉世苏武是也。今当令公归位之期，不免在此点化于他。待我点化一座庙"
        },
        {
          "character": "苏武",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "宇，一座碑牌，再变一只老羊。远远望见令公来也！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（杨继业上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨继业",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "当年路过五台山，"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨继业",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "智空长老对我言。"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨继业",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "到如今果应了智空言。"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨继业",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "他道我在两狼山前遭围困"
        },
        {
          "character": "老丈",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "请了！"
        },
        {
          "character": "苏武",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "请了！"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨继业",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "请问老丈，此地是什么所在？"
        },
        {
          "character": "苏武",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "此地是我庄，庄前是两狼。虎口交牙峪，犯者一命亡！"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨继业",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "老丈在此做些什么？"
        },
        {
          "character": "苏武",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "在此牧羊。"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨继业",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "这样兵荒马乱，你还牧的什么羊啊？"
        },
        {
          "character": "苏武",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "兵荒不兵荒，与我却无妨。老汉无别干，在此牧老羊。"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨继业",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "这老羊有什么贵处呢？"
        },
        {
          "character": "苏武",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "慢道老羊无贵样，提起老羊甚惨伤。生下几个羊羔子，轰轰烈烈在世上。"
        },
        {
          "character": "苏武",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "今日几个死，明日几个亡。老汉掐指算，今日死老羊。"
        },
        {
          "character": "苏武",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "老羊！老羊！还不与我死！"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨继业",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "呀呸！"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨继业",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "老丈说话理不通，"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨继业",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "句句说的杨令公。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（苏武接刀下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨继业",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "狂风一阵影无踪。"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨继业",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "且住！一阵狂风，老丈不见，又将我的宝刀收去。有道是：为大将者，能舍千"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨继业",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "军，不舍寸铁。待我找上前去。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（杨继业走小圆场。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨继业",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "来此已是苏武庙，待我进去看来。那旁有一碑碣，待我看来。“李陵碑”，呀"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨继业",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "呀呸！想这李陵乃是背主求荣之人，是何人与他立这碑碣在此？上面还有几行"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨继业",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "小字，待我看来。"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨继业",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "“庙是苏武庙，碑是李陵碑。令公来到此，卸甲又丢盔。”"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨继业",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "且住！这诗句分明是指点于我。想我被困在两狼山——"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨继业",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "白日受饥饿，夜晚受风吹。盼兵兵不到，盼子子不归。"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨继业",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我何必等到冻饿而死，也罢！不免拜谢宋王爵禄之恩，就碰死在这李陵碑下！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（杨继业碰壁，死。四番兵、韩延寿同上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "韩延寿",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "呜呼呀！原来是老令公碰死李陵碑下。"
        },
        {
          "character": "韩延寿",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "巴图鲁，将他尸体搭了下去！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（四番兵搭杨继业同下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "韩延寿",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "待我报与太后知道便了！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（韩延寿下。）"
        }
      ],
